        stopCosts - An array of 4 costs for stopping on the Animal (Level 0 - 3).

        Parameters:

      • upgrade

        public void upgrade​(Player actor)
             throws AnimalNotOwnedException,
                    javax.naming.NoPermissionException,
                    AnimalUpgradeNotAllowedException
        Attempts to upgrade an Animal to the next level.

        You should always try to check if the Animal can be upgraded first using `Animal.isUpgradable(player)`.

        Parameters:
        actor - The Player attempting to upgrade the Animal.
        Throws:
        AnimalNotOwnedException - Thrown when the Animal isn't owned.
        javax.naming.NoPermissionException - Thrown when a Player other than the Animal owner attempts to upgrade the Animal.
        AnimalUpgradeNotAllowedException - Thrown when an Animal is already at the maximum level.
